title: Vinitharya
text:
1.  REDIRECT Eldacar

VINITHARYA is the original name of Eldacar, twenty-first King of Gondor
and son of Valacar and Vidugavia's daughter Vidumavi. He was originally
raised under this name before returning with his father to Gondor.

title: Óin(disambiguation)
text:
1.  REDIRECT Óin

was a dwarf who accompanied Bilbo on his quest in the hobbit. He is also a member of Thorin and Co. He is Glóin's brother and Gimli's uncle. He also seemed to be good friends with Balin, who recruited Óin to join him in establishing Moria. He was killed along the way
